===========================
gedit-code-assistance 0.3.0
===========================

This release issues a major change in how gedit-code-assistance works. The
code-assistance backends have been refactored as out-of-process dbus services
in a new project called gnome-code-assistance. The gedit-code-assistance project
now uses gnome-code-assistance services to provide code assistance for gedit
as a plugin.

